# =============================================================================
# File: /opt/ansible-k3s-cluster/README.failure-modes
# =============================================================================
# Purpose:
#   Document known failure modes for distributed builds, kernel deployments,
#   and cluster operations. This file helps diagnose issues quickly.
#
# Failure Modes:
#
#   1. distcc Not Distributing Jobs
#      - PATH incorrect
#      - DISTCC_HOSTS missing or wrong
#      - distccd not running on nodes
#
#   2. Kernel Deployment Fails
#      - Missing artifacts on builder
#      - Permissions incorrect on /boot
#      - Modules directory mismatch
#
#   3. Node Fails to Boot
#      - Incorrect kernel config
#      - Missing DTB
#      - Corrupted /boot
#
#   4. k3s Not Starting
#      - Missing overlay or br_netfilter
#      - Modules not loaded
#
#   5. SD Card Corruption
#      - Read-only rootfs
#      - ext4 errors in dmesg
#
# Notes:
#   - Update this file as new failure modes are discovered.
# =============================================================================
